CITY BANK FARMERS TRUST COMPANY, as Trustee under an Agreement Dated July 17, 1929, with Joseph H. Franzen (now Deceased), Appellant, v. ÆTNA LIFE INSURANCE COMPANY, Appellee. No. 116. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. March 5, 1934. Mitchell, Taylor, Capron & Marsh, of New York City (George S. M'ittendorf and Arnold Burst, both of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. James B. Henney, of New York City (Daniel Miner, of New York City, of counsel) , for appellee.

Before L. HAND, SWAN, and AUGUSTUS N. HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CUBIAM.

Judgment affirmed.
